name: Dardin_Shull
content:
Dardin Shull was a human male who lived on the planet Tatooine. In 9 BBY, Shull was present in a town square in Anchorhead when Inquisitors Third Sister and Fifth Brother interrogated the locals for information regarding the fugitive Jedi Nari.
Dardin Shull lives on Tatooine and gives water to the locals in a stand. One day, he was giving water to people until foreman Groff Ditcher cut in line. Reva returns to Tatooine and ask him where Owen Lars was. Dardin found Owen and his nephew: Luke Skywalker in a store and came to warn Owen that Reva was looking for him.
Dardin Shull, portrayed by Hossein Mardani, first appeared in "Part I," the first episode of the Obi-Wan Kenobi television series.
